trans-unit.source: Provides programmatic access to the context of the outgoing Web request.
Gets and sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Accept" name="Accept" href=""></xref> header value from the outgoing Web request.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Accept" name="Accept" href=""></xref> header from the outgoing Web request.
Gets and sets the content length header value of the outgoing Web request.
The content length header of the outgoing Web request.
Gets and sets the content type header value from the outgoing Web request.
The content type header from the outgoing Web request.
Gets the headers for the outgoing Web request.
A <xref:System.Net.WebHeaderCollection> instance that contains the headers of the outgoing Web request.
Gets and sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_IfMatch" name="IfMatch" href=""></xref> header value from the outgoing Web request.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_IfMatch" name="IfMatch" href=""></xref> header from the outgoing Web request.
Gets and sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_IfModifiedSince" name="IfModifiedSince" href=""></xref> header value from the outgoing Web request.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_IfModifiedSince" name="IfModifiedSince" href=""></xref> header from the outgoing Web request.
Gets and sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_IfNoneMatch" name="IfNoneMatch" href=""></xref> header value from the outgoing Web request.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_IfNoneMatch" name="IfNoneMatch" href=""></xref> header from the outgoing Web request.
Gets and sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_IfUnmodifiedSince" name="IfUnmodifiedSince" href=""></xref> header value from the outgoing Web request.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_IfUnmodifiedSince" name="IfUnmodifiedSince" href=""></xref> header from the outgoing Web request.
Gets the HTTP method of the outgoing Web request.
The HTTP method of the outgoing Web request.

Gets a value that indicates whether [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] omits data that is normally written to the entity body of the response and forces an empty response to be returned.

If <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] omits any data that is normally written to the entity body of the response and forces an empty response to be returned.
Gets the user agent header value from the outgoing Web request.
The user agent header from the outgoing Web request.
